reviews.review_text: The service is fast and the food served is always fresh and hot. The self order checkout are easy to use and are always clean. The crew their is friendly and make sure that we understand what food we need and sometimes gives suggestions of what is better option. The dine in is cozy and wide especially in the sunshine it looks fabulous.

I usually pass by this McDonalds on the way to work using their mobile app which is very convenient. I usually use the drive-thru. The place looks neat and clean and the crew are very friendly, especially. Susan D Which is a delight to hear her in the drive-thru speaker and the window when youre passing through. Their coffee is very good as well as their muffins

The service is fast and the food served is always fresh and hot. The self order checkout are easy to use and are always clean. The crew their is friendly and make sure that we understand what food we need and sometimes gives suggestions of what is better option. The dine in is cozy and wide especially in the sunshine it looks fabulous. Recently they were giving free samples for their new ice cream and it was yummm. The parking lot has nice flowers and space for parking cars is wide. If I am nearby, I always get an ice cream for sure from here. The patio here though small is good for sitting during summer times.

google keeps asking me to review McDonalds even though this review means nothing to everyone everywhere. You all have an opinion on McDonalds and a strangers words on the internet isnt going to change that. I have attached a photo of one of my orders. I like ordering decaf completely black to see how the cashiers respond to the abomination. Thank you

Social distancing and limited seating in effect. Hand sanitizer at entrance/exit. Arrows to indicate traffic flow one way. Plexiglass shields at cashier as well as food pick up counter. All great safety measures to make you feel safe while ordering or eating here. Update:  service/atmosphere has gone downhill since reopening. Was there Friday night and took well over 6-7min to get my order. I ordered on the app. Restaurant was a mess. I could see kitchen was a mess too with fries all over the floor of the fry station. Staff was standing around chatting in kitchen and in no rush to serve customers. By the way, my fries were cold too. Very disappointed.
This place is well organized, very clean and with great customer service. First time 5 stars for McDonalds.

I bought for my kids lunch here a double burger and a happymeal.  But when I brought it home my son found it was a single burger. When I went to them the next day with a complaint, the administrator gave me a double burger and happymeal for free. A very positive experience. Thanks to the restaurant and manager.
Good placefor quick lunch and treat myself at the middle of the day.
good location, I have ordered McFish this time.. I can say it was not the freshest fried pattie, but I understand it was around 1.15am.. so no regrets.. it satisfied me and thats all what matter
Something about music list, whoever picked those songs, it s all contemporary and amazing as to make me stay for long and write reviews Cheers Food

Im giving this McDonalds 5 stars simply because I needed to blow my nose after getting off the bus and having to get on the SkyTrain.  Why didnt I just go to the Timmies literally just a few steps away right across the street from the SkyTrain station you ask?  Oh I did.  But sadly at 730am they had no toilet paper in their public washroom.  So, wtg, McDonalds!!; One more runny nose saved.  Thank you.
We went through the drive-thru and the attendant that was there, at about 9:00pm yesterday was really friendly and happy. The burger was made with care and was very full. Delightful experience.

Good food at reasonable prices and lots of free parking. Good for families on a budget especially when traveling or visiting Vancouver. Includes a playground for children. Vegetarian options: Special request menus available Dietary restrictions: Requests for special orders with extra veggies or salads are available Parking: Large lot for parking and other free parking on Southside of resturant Kid-friendliness: Lots of room for families and large seating areas, including playground. Wheelchair accessibility: Fully available
The time of your life. Amazing hamburger dish called a big mac. Im loving it. EAT IT. EAT THE THING. they also serve breakfast now. Im a physicist. Free refills kinda blew my mind. Food
When its raining and you just want some good vibes #McVibes
Excellent drive thru experience!! Fast and accurate order taking. Smiling faces order was perfectly placed in the bag. A, 7 star experience for sure!! Keep up the good work!!
Pretty convenient location. Friendly staff, 24 hours, so late night munchies are well taken care of.

Typical McDonalds franchise with a busy drive-through and large dine in area. Located on the busy Grandview Highway just down from the sky train station. This location is always exceedingly busy. Probably because of its excellent location close to transit and car thoroughfares. We went through drive-through today and even though the lineups were extensive through the double drive-through, service was efficient and accurate and the food was hot. What more can you expect from this staple of modern life?  Will come again.

We went by on the drive thru at 11pm, and the lady was so patient with us, even though we took forever to choose. Im very impressed by the customer service this late at night and with so many people lining up! Ill be coming back :))
Service was excellent and quality of food was great!

Small cafe with fresh food. Great quality and portion. I felt safe in there because they had the plexiglass installed in between tables. I ordered latte with oat milk and the crab cake brunch and chicken and bacon sandwich. Satisfied.

This was the first time I came for a visit with my friend. We  order two combos of fish burger and dine in there. The place was well cleaned and cozy.  We sat down, washed our hands in the washroom. Not for a while, the manager handed the meals to us with a smiling face. The food  was hot and delicious. Good to try again.

Take advantage of the awards points they offer check the app each day for new deals  . The workers are always very nice and pleasant  . Coffee muffin deal is the best with everything going up this pairing is the best option
Usually order from doordash here. Orders are always correct and arrive pretty fast, great job to all the workers here, it cant be easy getting everything done so fast in such a popular location.

For some reason the mcflurry in this mcdonalds costs less than the other mcdonalds I went to on that same day! This McDonalds also has more modern chairs and tables than some of the other ones Ive been to as they renovated a few years back.
Always clean, food comes out fresh and fast. Only knock off one star because the fries arent overfilling haha.
This is the most liminal McDonalds. 5 stars.

Best service around. These employees deserve a raise! On an extremely busy night they worked amazing as a team, were quick, efficient and werent messing up any orders. Plus they were cheering eachother on for doing a good job and getting through the rush and they deserve the claps
I had a Quarter Pounder BLT with large fries and a Coke. It was delicious. Tasty convenient food in a friendly atmosphere. Nice professional staff too.
They didn t have the item I asked but the guy in the front was very nice and gave me different options instead

Recently remodelled. Lots of kiosks not enough staff. Can take up to 10 minutes if you order during busy times.  Pickup area gets chaotic.  I dont like to get the toys with the Happy meals but they always include it. They try and have better managers than other locations.

i usually just order on skip, but i stopped at this location on my way home late around 11pm. I just want to say the two employees working, were very friendly and seemed to be enjoying doing their job.  Its often rare now days with covid and all, I just want to say thank you and keep up the good work LOL

Extremely polite young teens at drive thru. Way to go teens. So nice to see young people working hard and dispelling myths that they as a generation are video game addicts, rude and self centered with no manners. Keep up the good work McDonalds, and teens. It is well appreciated and noted

Very nice & cozy fast food restaurants. The staff at this McDonalds are very friendly & efficient compared to other locations. No fuss delicious hot & freshly prepared food. This is the first time in 15 years I have been served piping hot food to eat. Ideally,, by the time I get to my table, or the food gets brought to me in the car from Drive through, it is cold, the coffee tastes like Luke warm water & the pop is out of Gas. No wonder I hated McDonalds fast food. Believe me I truely enjoyed my meal today. Infact because I really enjoyed my meal today, we sat & also enjoyed Apple pies as an extra treat. I definately recommend all to try out this location, you will never again return to all those problem locations again. Very neat & cleans, no over flowing garbage bins or even a single dirty table, where customers had to clean, before eating their meals. Every single point at this location, was past excellent. Thank you McDonalds Restaurants.

Its McDonalds, so you know it is what it is. I didnt realise they dont sell their big salads anymore so thats kind of a bummer. The food was hot, fresh and fast. I got two cheese burgers and a poutine... the poutine has cheese curd! and a vanilla ice coffee. Overall happy with my order.
Completely surprising service. They were fast, polite, friendly, and best of all, got our entire order correct on the first attempt. For a second I almost thought I wasnt at a McDonalds!!
There are some great staff working here.
Great food, great service

My favorite McDonalds restaurant. They train all of the managers here and they always have all of the toys available for Happy Meals here because it is the head office. You will get impeccable service and top notch food quality here. Of course its still a McDonalds fast food burger, but within that category, its the best experience. Also the dining area is open 24 hours which is nice.
Well its hard time , but I know youre doing well . I love McDonalds Restaurants.

Thank you midnight team for preparing my midnight meal lol You guys did a excellent job :) I always order from Skip during 1am or 2am, if you guys 12 order burger or bunch of muffin it s me !! You guys always made order really fast and accurate. And thank you so much for the free cookie

This McDonalds location goes out of their way to make EVERY customer feel special and ensure that all orders are awesome. Manager Marvin exemplifies excellent customer service beyond the call of duty.
Very convenient 24h service collect 7 stickers and get free coffee
Very fast service and friendly staff. I find their coffee tastes better than other locations. Perhaps coz of high volume and it being fresher?
They can make both good and bad food,  maybe they see if the person ordering has come out of a bentley or not. I swear I saw the manger looking at CCTV for same. She was nice to me though
Always a great experience, nice people, good food, good service. I love the LCD touch screens to order, and skipping the line while you just wait for your meal. Great idea McDonalds!
Fantastic dinner! The beef was tender, the potatoes cooked to perfection... I thought the drinks were pricey but this is how it goes in Vancouver...  I think it really impressed my date!
6 June 2020 For this particular visit, curb side pick up went smoothly and order was correct. I even got a heart shaped choco chip cookie. Good job team

Honestly the best McDonalds in the city. Its efficiently run, tons of leadership and management on hand. This is clearly a location that builds careers. Im just a customer, but Im always impressed with this location. I figured I should leave a positive review.
Its a McDonalds, what else is there to say? Super quick service, cheap, and tasty. Best hot $8 meal you can get.
Russel, the manager is very kind, compassionate, polite and down to earth person. He went above and beyond for me. McDonalds, you are lucky to have him.
Pretty good drive thru. Never any problems getting my order quickly during my lunch breaks.
really fast and the workers are nice food was good too
With app it was pretty nice since no need to remember to bring a paper coupon and could just park and wait for the food to be made.
Hottest coffee Ive ever had at any McDonalds friendly service, air conditioning to escape the heat from :D
The place is very good, they serve food fast, the allow you to get paper (not like the Metrotown one), the food isn t served messy, the best McDonald s I have been to.
I truly recommend this location the service is first class and the staff are very professional and friendly. Plus the sandwiches they make are a 10 out of 10. Im a customer from now on.
Very fast service had to take time to clean between each customers for covid-19 and you can actually eat inside this McDonalds nice.
Great experience with a big breakfast order for Nurses Week. Staff was friendly and accommodating. Everything went very smoothly. Would order there again.
Great place after renovation. Table service is cool. Each booth has an outlet, which is good for studying, pretty nice ambiance.
Love their McDoubles. It is amazing
Excellent open concept restaurant with bright and comfy seating areas. Very busy drive thru!
Unlike other locations they have a full menu of food available
You cant go wrong with Mcdonalds fast food but the staff is a hit and missed kind of service!
Love the coffee. Unbeatable coffee + muffin combo deal! Plz make coffee + bagel the same price as with muffin because muffins are probably really unhealthy.
Kulwinder singh is a best employee over here. He has quick capacity to deal all customers with very good manners.
I dont eat McDonalds very much, but the drive-thru service here is always SO friendly! Which I think is super rare for fast food places
Big parking lot and friendly staffs.  The drive thru lane is almost always busy but the staffs are fast and efficient, so you could expect to get in and out fast.
One of the best McD locations Ive been to. Very busy but always well staffed and prompt service.
Ordered from mobile for pickup in the parking lot. My order was finished in a jiffy. Very satisfied with the service at this location!
The usual mcd menu but very clean including bathrooms, plenty of dining space + drive thru & mobile order, uber eats. also plenty machine kiosks and friendly & professional staff
Amazing staff always go the extra mile, even sending an extra treat and leaving nice notes on the bag for delivery orders!
Im totally impressed
I love that these guys are flexible and willing to lettuce wrap my burgers for me. Good price fast food and pleasant service.
What can I say that hasnt been said by others? Great for a quick junk food fix. Their McChicken burgers went downhill since the beginning.
One of my favorite McDonalds.. clean, well lit and friendly staff. Bathroom is quite clean (compared with others).
If youre going to eat here, make sure its through the drive through. In-store visit is a no no unless you feel like being harassed.
Its McDonald, you get what you get from here.  If you dont know what McDonald s is all about, you should probably climb out from underneath the rock you been living under.
didn t screw up order got my nuggies
Michael Song is the best !!! So patient, kind and makes sure all your sauce needs are taken care of. #sauceitup
Central location. Bad or no service. 20 mins waiting time for both drive thru and dine in.
Fast and efficient service. Drive through can be crowded at times but its not a fault of the establishment.
The place is clean & beautiful after renovation.  Staff are friendly & so efficient.   Not bad at all!
Fast food as expected
Service was meh but the icecream was on point
I recommend the hamburger. Also, poor choice of hats at this location.
The place is always really clean. They have a lot of the touchscreen ordering stations as well.
This is seriously a great McDonalds. From the Manager Ricky on down, the most consistantly high quality McDonalds Ive been to in a long while.
I love
hasnt been too ghetto for me yet. They allowed me in even when my head was covered with saran wrap during a late night hair dyeing day.
old work place has received an update.  comple renovation
Nice employees, but its one of the most busiest McDs I have been to.
Clark is somewhat satisfied with the sturdier eco straws that are employed at this particular restaurant
Store is spacious but sometimes noisy. 24 hour open so you can come anytime.
I dont know why but I like this McDonalds even though I feel like crap after eating it. Having breakfast here once in a while is a guilty pleasure.
Always a fast and efficient service at this store! Thanks a congrats to the team
Night crew is very nice , very fast service and polite especially the manager sukh  very polite.
They are bringing food out faster than normal. Good work!
A very clean McDonalds. They have the new electronic order machines. Orders are made quickly.
Very close-by, so a good place to get my fast food fix.
